summary: I know it's coming, but I'm still not ready

There’s really gonna be people out here thinking Captain Marvel is stronger than Diana of Themyscira? Like wow don’t let the movies (I love them) fool y'all, my sis Diana isn’t scared of some photon blast or a little binary.
